name: Atlas Air 747-446 Landing at Calgary Airport
description:
Hello everyone, this is an Atlas Air Boeing 747-400 landing at Calgary International Airport, operating a charter for the Royal Air Force. This was the first time I've ever seen a passenger 747 in Calgary, so it was pretty exciting to see. Enjoy the video, and please watch in 1080p! 

Thanks for watching, please comment, rate, and subscribe! More videos are coming soon.
